Dear Michael Gary Scott ,
Thank you for applying for a new career opportunity within SAP. After carefully reviewing your application, we regret to inform you that we have chosen to pursue other applicants. But, this doesn’t have to be the end of the road.
We invite you to continue your search and set up a job agent in the SAP Career Center to learn about future opportunities.

Best Regards, 
SAP Talent Attraction

Hi Micheal Gary Scott,
Thank you for your interest in the Quantitative Analyst role at Affirm! Unfortunately we just hired someone for this role, so the position is no longer available.
We recognize there are many options out there, and we want you to know we genuinely value your interest in working here. In line with our core value that People Come First at Affirm, we are invigorated by your interest in revamping the consumer financial industry for all and would love to stay in touch as we grow. Our company is constantly evolving, and there may be a position available for you down the line.
Wishing you the best of luck in your job search!
Thanks again!
Affirm Talent Team

Hi Michael Gary Scott
We appreciate you taking the time to apply for a position at Fable. Although we strive to respond to each applicant individually, if you don't hear from us within a few weeks, please consider it a temporary rejection. However, there's always a possibility of a perfect match in the future.
We also recommend following us on for updates. We're pretty great (but we might be biased).
Hope to chat soon!
Fable's Talent Acquisition Team

Hi Michael Gary Scott ,
We really appreciate the time and effort you invested in your application for the position of Jr Data Analyst here at Just Eat Takeaway.com.
After carefully comparing your profile to other candidates and our needs for this vacancy, we unfortunately need to inform you that we will not proceed with your application at this moment.
Unfortunately, we are not able to provide individual feedback to your application this early in our recruitment process.
Although this opportunity didn’t work out, we really hope you’ll be able to find another role which interests you on careers.justeattakeaway.com. If you would like ongoing updates on news and opportunities at Just Eat Takeaway.com, you're welcome to sign up to our Talent Community.
We wish you all the best with your job search!
Best wishes,
Talent Acquisition at Just Eat Takeaway.com
